{"tid":682574,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"去日本除左行街睇景點仲有咩做","createTime":"2018-05-29T03:40:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-29T11:47:49.000Z","uid":86762,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"7b90027c7e4ade42469693961672b3edb279d31d","tid":682574,"uid":86762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T03:40:02.000Z","msg":"肯定有人答叫雞 所以我幫你講咗先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n嚟緊下個禮拜去3個人去大阪 京都同東京<br />\n行程plan咗七成 但係淨低嗰啲唔想再行街或者睇景點 想揾下其他嘢做 <br />\n<br />\n已有浸溫泉, 參加祭典, 去vr體驗館<br />\n( 對博物館,睇動物,去主題公園興趣不大)<br />\n仲有咩介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n題外話 <br />\n喺京都夜晚可以做咩? 5點打後<br />\n<br />\nThanks <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68997f61c5a07254585fe0fd490691e9dbe939bf","tid":682574,"uid":21423,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T03:42:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4f43baa54ccc3c60559004bab6411b4f03dabfb5","tid":682574,"uid":6604,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T03:49:27.000Z","msg":"去稚內"},{"pid":"eaddb89b491115e3c6b53b7afb19c0a5c378614b","tid":682574,"uid":155197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T03:50:07.000Z","msg":"坐飛機"},{"pid":"4313290ca118685c2793ed82581bfd1e414b6e24","tid":682574,"uid":86762,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T03:50:52.000Z","msg":"漏咗講<br />\n5日大阪(其中1日去姬路城) <br />\n1日京都(住1晚)<br />\n4日東京"},{"pid":"347969ab4ec429e3f25227bdb7db1f589b6b2ec0","tid":682574,"uid":3273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T03:51:37.000Z","msg":"飛車"},{"pid":"7f923edf50ce0f36612015aca39f343735689773","tid":682574,"uid":86762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f43baa54ccc3c60559004bab6411b4f03dabfb5","tid":682574,"uid":6604,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"